  "page": "Feature quote/243",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>He dreamt an old dream, of three <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">knights in white cloaks</a>, and a <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Joy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tower of Joy\">tower long fallen</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna</a> in her bed of blood. —<a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>'s fever dream<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_39\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 39\">Chapter 39</a>, Eddard X.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403215113\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 83/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8402/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 303/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 177/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.389      1 -total\n100.00%    5.389      1 Template:Ref\n 67.81%    3.654      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26761-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403215113 and revision id 2468